<div id="pf45" class="pf w0 h0" data-page-no="45"><div class="pc pc45 w0 h0"><img class="bi x68 y240 w14 h2a" alt="" src="bg45.png"/><div class="t m0 x22 h7 y19 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">寻觅失落的文明<span class="ff13"> <span class="fs4 lsc"> 67 </span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h1 y1a ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m0 xd h1 y1b ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5e ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">大家不要互相排斥。佛弟子</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y4c ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">之间的互相排斥、诋毁和攻</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y4d ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">击，<span class="_ _c"></span>不但会给佛教带来危害，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y4e ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">也会成为自己修行的障碍。</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5f ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">我们应该对所有教派观清净</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y60 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">心，对佛陀无垢的密意生起</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y61 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">信解，这种认识是不可缺少</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y62 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">的。 </div><div class="t m0 x21 h4 y53 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls62 ws0">虽然在有些人群中，各</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y54 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">教派还有另一种名字——宁</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y55 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">玛派是红教，<span class="_ _c"></span>格鲁派是黄教，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y238 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">萨迦派是花教，噶举派是白</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y241 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">教等等，但这与其本身的特</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y242 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">色毫不相关。 </div><div class="t m0 x1c h4 y243 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls2e ws0">以前华智仁波切到一个寺院，有个喇嘛问他：<span class="_ _c"></span><span class="ls29">“你是什</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y5a ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls4b ws0">么教的？”他回答：<span class="_ _c"></span><span class="ls1b">“佛教。<span class="_ _c"></span><span class="ls63">”喇嘛生气了：<span class="_ _21"></span><span class="ls64">“我问的不是这</span></span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yfa ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">个，<span class="_ _21"></span>问你是戴黄帽子的还是红帽子的<span class="_ _12"></span><span class="fs4">（意思是黄教还是红教）<span class="_ _12"></span><span class="fs3">？”</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yfb ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">华智仁波切心平气和地从怀里掏出一顶破烂的灰色羊皮帽，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yfc ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">说道：<span class="_ _1f"></span>“我没有红、<span class="_ _8"></span>黄帽子，<span class="_ _6"></span>只有这顶灰帽子。<span class="_ _c"></span>”<span class="_ _6"></span>他含蓄地表</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yfd ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">示，自己不偏堕于任何教派。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
